                                                          Volcanus The Fire lord
Starting stats 10 strenght, 10 agility, 16 inteillgence, Stats gain per level, 0.30 Strenght, 0.50 Agility, 1.00 Inteillgence.
Base movespeed 265, Base attack damage 4-9, Base Regeneration Health 0.4, Base Regeneration Mana 0.8.

total base stats at level 40 - 22 Strenght - 30 Agility - 56 Inteillgence -

Volcanus spells will have insane mana cost early game and so on.
Leving up Incinerate once can be great but maxing it first can be a problem since it does better damage late game with the inteillgence
burn scaling and for the explosion as well.

LEVEL 30 TALENT

Talent 1
Increase Volcanus Health by 15% and his magic resist by 10%
Volcanus will gain 0.1 health regeneration per 30 health missing and every 2% health missing he will gain 0.7 armor. further Increase
Volcano damage reduction by 25% he cannot be Interrupted. Volcanus will reduce Silence duration by 40% and Stuns duration by 25%, he
further increase those bonus by 10% while in Fire Rage.


Talent 2 
Increase Volcanus spell amp by 8% and his mana regeneration by 3.2
Volcanus will gain 0.1% spellamp per 0.4 mana regeneration and his 3 Basic spells will also deal 10% bonus damage base on his Strenght
and Agility, Volcanus Lava Wave will have 115 radius increase and Soul Burn will have 1.0 seconds duration increase. Volcanus will
gain 1% coldown reduction for every 5% mana missing and he also gain 4 more mana from inteillgence.


PASSIVE D OR F Fire Lord
Increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff, pressing Alt will show the level 40 talent of this and level 30 talent.

BUFF Volcanus attack will do magic damage instead of physical and he gain 1% spellamp per 6 int instead of 10 and he can use 2 glove
Intead of 1 he also gain 2 life per inteillgence point any Roots will be purge and give Volcanus 25% spellamp for 4.2 seconds, the purge
will only happen every 25 seconds. he can also use Sulfuras, getting even more power from it but making him become melee range.

DEBUFF Volcanus will take 40% more damage from pure,physical and magic damage and he cannot use any weapons but gloves as weapons
he also lose 40% base attack damage and all Source of Physical damage will deal 1.2% of Volcanus life as damage bonus to him and
magical Source of damage will do 0.6% bonus damage as well, Volcanus will lose 25% mana regeneration source and his spells will only
gain 50% of Spellvamp bonus effect as well.


talent level 40 upgrade Fire Lord
add a new modfier Titan of Fire
Spawn 2 Greater Lava Spawn that last until they die, they will respawn every 75 seconds close to Volcanus, they cannot Recreate other
Lava Spawns. Volcanus Soul Burn will always have 275 Area of Effect instead of being a single target (stack it self with Fire Rage) and
Volcano will always throw Lava Balls to target inside the Radius of Volcano it self every 1.5 seconds, those Lava Balls will deal 35%
increase damage and will deal pure damage and will also make enemys take 20% increase damage from Pure damage and Volcano it self. Volcanus
can no longet be slowed, instead he will turn the slow into a buff that give Volcanus 20% spellamp and 120 movespeed for 3.6 seconds.
Doesnt have a coldown.

GREATER LAVA SPAWN STATS Attack Range 385
health 425 plus 25% of Volcanus health
Mana 200 plus 15% of Volcanus mana
Armor 13
Magic resist 42%
damage 21-37 plus 18% of Volcanus Int
Base attack time 2.15

SPELL Q Molten Breath of Lava
The Greater Lava Spawn will breath out Lava dealing high magical damage to any target in a 335 cone infront of the Lava Spawn and also
giving them a burn sickness, dealing low damage every 0.5 seconds and reducing their magical resistence as well. The Magical Resistence
lost will increase every time they suffer the burn damage. Molten Breath of Lava will gain 45% of the Lava Spawn attack damage into bonus
damage. The Burn damage can be refresh by other Greater Lava Spawn increasing the amount of magical resistence lost. The Burn damage will
be Pure damage and will gain 4% of the Lava Spawn attack damage into bonus damage.

base damage 45
Burn damage 6
base magic resist lost 4%
magic resist lost per burn damage 1%
burn damage duration 3.5 seconds
coldown 27
mana cost 175

Passive Pure Molten Coating
The Greater Lava Spawn will burn nearby enemys (280 radius) every 0.8 seconds dealing Medium Pure damage and also making them take extra
damage from Pure damage Source. Pure Molten Coating damage cannot be resisted and for every 2% pure resist on the target, it will deal
1% increase damage. The Burn damage will gain 10% of the Greater Lava Spawn attack damage into bonus damage. Stack with other Greater
Lava Spawn.

base damage 12
Extra Pure damage taken 10%


SPELL Q
Soul Burn - Magical -
Volcanus curse his target Dealing damage every 1.0 second and also reducing attack damage, slowing and also silencng them for the duration.
Soul Burn cannot be Purge by anymeans and will Ignore spell immune units, the duration will have 2.0 seconds increase if the target lose
at least 30% of his max health durring its duration. If the target was Slowed before Soul Burn was casted on them, it will deal 175%
190% 205% 220% of Volcanus inteillgence in a 475 area of effect burst damage once on the target.

damage 13 17 21 25 plus 13% 17% 21% 25% of intelligence
damage reduction 11% 22% 33% 44%
movespeed slow 10% 14% 18% 22%
duration 5
cooldown 16
mana cost 70 110 150 190 plus 3% of max mana

Talent level 10 upgrade Soul Burn
increase scaling damage by 10%
increase slow amount by 14%
increase duration by 1.0
reduce coldown by 1
remove mana cost

add a new modfier Sun Burn
Soul Burn will silence all enemy near the main target 350 radius and Soul Burn got 20% chance to deal 50% increase damage and dealing
pure damage, after Soul Burn duration end it will explode for 300% of Volcanus inteillgence to all near enemys 425 radius, Volcanus will
gain 1% spell amp for every 6 seconds of Soul Burn done, at 6% spell amp bonus, Soul Burn will gain 5 base damage and 10% increase slow
at 11% spell amp bonus, Soul Burn will do Small Burns that deal 14% of Incinerate total damage every 0.5 seconds and reduce the coldown
by 3, at 16% spell amp bonus, Volcanus will gain 12% max health and mana, Soul Burn will deal its damage every 0.7 seconds instead of 1.0
seconds, max stack of 20% spell amp bonus, 10 stacks are lost upon death and 1 stack is lost upon getting slowed. Volcanus will also deal
35% increase attack damage and 25 bonus attack speed on the target affected by Soul Burn.

SPELL W Lava Wave - Magical -
Send out a wave of molten lava dealing insane amount of damage and burning them dealing damage every 0.5 seconds and reduce their
magical resistence for the duration of the Burn. Lava Wave will gain 50% increase bonus from spellamp but will cost 0.02% more mana
for every spellamp Volcanus has.

damage 25 40 55 70 plus 35% of inteillgence
burn damage 10 plus 8% of inteillgence
magic resist lost 8% 12% 16% 20%
