talent level 10 upgrade Lava Wave
increase inteillgence scaling by 15%
increase Burn inteillgence scaling by 3%
increase magic resist lost by 6%
increase Wave radius by 55
Increase mana cost by 45

add a new modfier Scorched Earth
Lava Wave will leave behind a Scorched Earth giving enemys that enter it the Burn damage and increasing the magic resist lost by 10%
while they stand in it, Volcanus will get heal by 200% of Burn total damage if he stand it in and also gaining 10% damage reduction and
1.5 mana regeneration. For every 10 enemys hit with Lava have increase the travel distence by 3, at 20 stacks Lava wave will gain 15
bonus base damage and have 25% mana cost reduce, at 35 stacks Lava wave will have 50% chance to double the Burn duration and increase
Volcanus mana by 225, at 50 Stacks Volcanus will throw 3 Waves instead of 1, each dealing the same amount of damage but dealing 40%
reduce damage if the target is hit again by aother Lava Wave and increase Volcanus spell amp by 10%. The Scorched Earth Burn will damage
every 1.0 seconds instead of 0.5 seconds and it will last 6 seconds.


SPELL E Volcano - Magical -
Volcanus Channel a Volcano for 6 7 8 9 seconds, each 1.0 seconds the Volcano will throw Lava Balls at random in its radius dealing
high magical damage and Ministuning enemys for 0.1. They will take increase damage from Volcanus spells every time they get damage form
Volcano and Volcanus will gain 15% damage reduction while he is Channeling. The Amount of lava Balls will increase by 1 for every 17
inteillgence. the extra damage taken will refresh if they are hit again by a Lava Ball, the debuff duration will last 4.5 seconds.
The radius of Volcano will tell where the Lava Balls will land and those Lava Balls have 225 plus 150% of Volcanus inteillgence for
their impact radius and also increase the Volcano radius by 150% 175% 200% 225% of Volcanus inteillgence. Durring the channel of
Volcano, it will drain Volcanus mana by 3 6 9 12 every 0.5 seconds.

damage 16 22 28 34 plus 40% of Inteillgence
base Amount of Lava Balls 6 9 12 15
base Volcano Radius 550 625 700 775
extra damage taken 1.2% 1.5% 1.8% 2.1%
coldown 28
mana cost 50 100 150 200 plus 5% of max mana

talent level 20 upgrade Volcano
increase inteillgence scaling by 25%
increase the amount of lava balls by 3
increase the damage taken by 0.9%
remove max mana cost

add a new modfier Reborn to Lava
The Volcano will Debuff the enemys with Lava Creation for 3.5 seconds, upon death enemys will spawn a Lava Spawn with their own stats
and 2 passive. Only 4 can be alive and they will last 70 seconds. Volcano will also do a Explosion after Volcanus stop Channeling for at
least 3 seconds, 50% of Volcano radius will be the Explosion dealing 30 plus 75% of inteillgence in magical damage and giving enemys
Soul Burn with all of its effect but also having 3.0 seconds duration reduce. Volcanus will gain 5 health for every Lava Spawn Created
at 50 health gain, increase volcanus health by 10% and health regeneration by 3.5. at 150 health gain, Volcano will have 20 base damage
bonus and increase Volcanus health regeneration Source by 30% and reduce the duration of healing source reduction by 25%. Max of 200
health gain and he lose all of them on death. The Lava Spawn cannot be controlled and will follow Volcanus around but can be click on
to see their passive effects and also casting spell on them.

LAVA SPAWN STATS Range 345
health 275 plus 13% of Volcanus health
no mana
Armor 9
Magic resist 22%
damage 11-27 plus 10% of Volcanus Int
Base attack time 1.85

Passive Living Lava
Enemys that come close to the Lava Spawn 265 radius will get burn for 2 plus 3% of Lava Spawn Attack damage every 0.4 seconds in Magical
damage that stack with the others Lava spawn as well. Also increase their Pure resist by 15% and increase this bonus by 1% for every 3
seconds they live

Passive Recreate
Lava Spawn will Create Smaller Lava Spawn after they deal 40% of their total Max health in damage with their Basic attack and Living
Lava to the enemys, They will Create 1 Smaller Lava Spawn with only 35% of their total stats they had, those smaller Version of them
self will not Recreate new one. Also refresh the duration of the Normal Lava Spawn duration to 70 again and the Smaller one with last
35 seconds. this can only happen 2 time


PASSIVE D OR F Incinerate
Increase Volcanus Agility, Strenght with Inteillgence and all of Volcanus spells will give 1 stacks of Incinerate every time they deal
damage, Incinerate will do burn damage every 1.5 seconds base on Volcanus Inteilgence and after 6 seconds if the target doesnt die,
Incinerate will explode dealing medium damage to nearby enemys and the target him self only work once for each targets. If they die,
Incinerate will also explode dealing same damage. Basic attack will also give enemys 1 stack of Incinerate. Incinerate will last 2.5
seconds and will deal Pure damage on the burn and explosion. Incinerate will gain 40% of Volcanus inteillgence in bonus radius for the
Explosion. Incinerate will also reduce the target healing sources by 15%.

Attributes bonus 7% 8% 9% 10%
Incinerate base burn damage 12% 16% 20% 24% of int
Incinerate bonus burn damage per stacks 1% of int
Incinerate max stacks 8 12 16 20
Incinerate explosion damage 10 15 20 25 plus 65% of inteillgence
base explosion radius 240 260 280 300

talent level 20 upgrade Incinerate
Increase base burn scaling by 10%
increase Incinerate burn stacks by 5
increase Incinerate explosion base damage by 10

add a new modfier Fire Blast
Incinerate will have 40% increase explosion radius and 20% increase damage if it explode under the 6 seconds marks, making the enemys
take 6 stacks of Incinerate as well they will also suffer a Fire Blast, Incinerate debuff will not go away and the target will gain 1
stack of Incinerate every seconds, at max stacks they will alway do Incinerate explosion every 2.5 seconds only dealing 40% of the
explosion total damage. If Volcanus dies, all target affected by Incinerate will end. Volcanus will gain 1 mana for every stacks of
Incinerate gain on enemys, at 125 mana bonus gain, Volcanus will gain 10% increase mana and will gain Phase movement, at 300 mana bonus
gain, Incinerate will give Volcanus 4% spellamp for every target affected by Incinerate and Volcanus will gain 15% magic resist, at 475
mana bonus gain, Incinerate will spreads to other target when the target dies or the explosion goes off after 6 seconds and also gaining
80 bonus radius. Max of 700 stacks and 60 stacks will be lost if Volcanus get silence and he will lose 350 stacks on death. Bosses will
lose the Incinerate debuff when they hit the max stack value.

ULTIMATE R
Fire Rage
Volcanus will triple in Size gaining massive health, attack damage, Spellamp and damage reduction but at the cost of not being able to
move for the duration. Volcanus will also Empower his 3 basic spells also reducing their coldown and making Incinerate get stronger too.
Soul Burn will be a 450 area of effect instead of being a single target and also having bonus damage, Lava Wave will gain insane bonus
damage and will become pure damage and the Burn will make enemys take extra Pure damage instead, Volcano will no longer be a Channeling
spells for the duration of Fire Rage and having more Lava Balls. Volcanus will gain 325 attack range with Sulfuras while in Fire Rage.
Incinerate will gain 10% 15% 20% increase total radius and will also have 8% 16% 24% base burn scalling increase for the duration of
Fire Rage

bonus health 25% 35% 45%
bonus attack damage 35 70 105
bonus spellamp 20% 30% 40%
bonus damage reduction 10% 15% 20%
coldown reduction 30% 40% 50%
Soul Burn bonus damage 8 11 14
Lava Wave bonus damage 30 55 70
Lava Balls bonus 6 9 12
duration 16 19 22
coldown 125
mana cost 25% 40% 55%

talent level 40 upgrade Fire Rage
increase bonus health by 25%
increase bonus attack damage by 55
increase damage reduction bonus by 5%
increase duration by 2
reduce coldown by 15

add a new modifier Hell Infuse
Volcanus will reduce all range attacks and spells damage taken to 35% (damage reduction and other source will not affect this) and he
also gain 15% spellvamp while in Fire Rage and his spells will have 25% chance to spellvamp for 175% of the damage dealt and give
Volcanus a Stack of Hell Infuse. Hell Infuse will give Volcanus 25 max health, 40 max mana, 1.2% spellamp and 15 bonus cast range max
stack of 10. At 3 stacks Volcanus will gain 15% status resistence with 0.1% health regeneration and also further increasing the duration
of Fire Rage by 4, at 7 stacks Volcanus will gain 15% magic resist with 0.2% mana regeneration and also increasing the health and spell
amp bonus gain from Fire Rage by 10%, at max stacks Volcanus will gain 10 Armor with 35% movespeed and also increasing his Fire Rage
damage reduction by 5% and the coldown reduction by 10%. The bonus from the stacks and the stacks its self will Double when in Fire Rage.
He also gain a spell call Hell Blink when in Fire Rage, Volcanus will be able to blink while in Fire Rage with a base cast range of 425
and a coldown of 14 seconds.

